Healthcare.Gov API Endpoint Classes

Source: R/S7_hgov.R
healthcaregov.Rd

Healthcare.Gov API Endpoint Classes

Usage

hgov_endpoint(alias)

hgov_temporal(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <hgov_endpoint>, or <hgov_temporal> object

Examples

hgov_endpoint("ab_registration_completion")
#> <hgov_endpoint>
#>  @ identifier: chr "https://data.healthcare.gov/api/1/datastore/query/wb6u-x2ny/0"
#>  @ metadata  :List of 6
#>  .. $ title      : chr "AB Registration Completion List"
#>  .. $ description: chr "Access Data Dictionary Here - https://www.cms.gov/CCIIO/Programs-and-Initiatives/Health-Insurance-Marketplaces/"| __truncated__
#>  .. $ periodicity: chr "Decennially [R/P10Y]"
#>  .. $ issued     : Date[1:1], format: "2016-03-30"
#>  .. $ modified   : Date[1:1], format: "2025-05-16"
#>  .. $ download   : chr "https://data.healthcare.gov/sites/default/files/uploaded_resources/TBL_RCL_140.csv"
#>  @ dimensions: <class_dimensions>
#>  .. @ limit : int 500
#>  .. @ rows  : int 1021083
#>  .. @ pages : int 2043
#>  .. @ fields:List of 7
#>  .. .. $ npn                                    : chr "npn"
#>  .. .. $ applicable_plan_year                   : chr "applicable_plan_year"
#>  .. .. $ individual_registration_completion_date: chr "individual_registration_completion_date"
#>  .. .. $ individual_marketplace_end_date        : chr "individual_marketplace_end_date"
#>  .. .. $ shop_registration_completion_date      : chr "shop_registration_completion_date"
#>  .. .. $ shop_end_date                          : chr "shop_end_date"
#>  .. .. $ npn_valid_current_plan_year_only       : chr "npn_valid_current_plan_year_only"
